br />\n其實中學畢業之後大家都冇乜聯絡<br />\n係fb有幾句咁<br />\n早兩三年社會不斷撕裂果陣<br />\n佢都幾乎日日屌人 (屌佔中 / 屌遊行 / 總之反政府就屌)<br />\n開頭有同佢理性討論下<br />\n後來好似比黨洗左腦咁好撚恐怖<br />\n我都都廢撚事理佢 直接unfollow佢就算<br />\n廢事佢D廢文出現係我FB度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb50afa74f96618211ce5825665b22e64ff0c3da","tid":122303,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你份友誼都幾膚淺，你咁諗即係冇當人係老友</blockquote><br />\n就係曾過先掙扎，唔熟嘅就一句屌你老母搞掂"},{"pid":"f5c64875ac008d9f592be959100d679fe61f42c8","tid":122303,"uid":50819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:06:27.000Z","msg":"道不同 不相為謀 志不同 不相為友"},{"pid":"c5403d2177156c18ec68a1b6c3a9acf474d66d77","tid":122303,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>歇盡所能 即係用盡能力蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n竭 同 歇 係完全相反嘅兩個字<br />\n竭力 vs 歇息<br />\n歇盡所能 即係 將所有能量用哂嚟歇息</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連號種LSC出品既CP所謂一哥都係咁既料，其他犬唔通真係近乎文盲定白癡？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢D小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />錯誤，我幾肯定小三TSA都唔撚會再考囉屌！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b7f4d1943c67c90d722fb6748413ad3f919b6a0b","tid":122303,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你份友誼都幾膚淺，你咁諗即係冇當人係老友</blockquote><br />\n當我係朋友既就咪撚做黑警</blockquote><br />\n我圍內食飯都講過邊個當差，我會絕交，半認真半講笑，誓估唔到係佢"},{"pid":"f9fb5eb15f65cc1719d4f821cce9d4be5fa3a1d6","tid":122303,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:07:23.000Z","msg":"你朋友都係窮途末路先揀做狗啫 又唔洗絕交嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9b306352857580d63a99fc7aa0be42b3ef69d7","tid":122303,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係黑警呢？你點諗？</blockquote><br />\n助長緊國家警察嘅勢力"},{"pid":"084c77d0040e078235d98fd0d24f2d07d73ef04e","tid":122303,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:08:05.000Z","msg":"應該 唔洗諗<br />\n揀得做黑警 就預左有後果 想又做雞又攞貞節牌坊?"},{"pid":"86d7c9ec1918a7b8feb849d913b5429b0979f0dc","tid":122303,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"連登答案係<br />\n但你仲視唔視人地係朋友，問自己問心就得"},{"pid":"670aeec6babf15128a1eae15651ad9102d5563ed","tid":122303,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你朋友都係窮途末路先揀做狗啫 又唔洗絕交嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假假地大學生，咁多紀律剖隊偏要做賊？"},{"pid":"0a0c37fe8446459f404d1dc9740443e40d3cc480","tid":122303,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係黑警呢？你點諗？</blockquote><br />\n雨革之後香港公安只有一種顏色"},{"pid":"a9e1a866dde2fa4444b5ea37ac4ff720aab9be40","tid":122303,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過屌佢老婆"},{"pid":"cdf6feec71bf03e134e9c9ccbebda21d6de4f36d","tid":122303,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:10:41.000Z","msg":"我都有個中學同學入左學堂，下星期畢業<br />\n佢之前約我食飯我都避開，話唔得閒算"},{"pid":"642db30116a9be1e07aa552d99bec4e63490029b","tid":122303,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"應"},{"pid