e3f92b1eb","tid":122303,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0787c6ca21f9344f85528281e8446c8543b597e1","tid":122303,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啫係咁你個fd去做警察 就即係變左黑警？<br />\n<br />\n理性少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 段友誼咁撚兒戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紀律部隊洗腦效率最高，佢地好快變曬支共既機械人，長痛不如短痛，絕交啦，做得黑警都係為錢多過為原則啦"},{"pid":"ff6389706d653036612f22f0e988866a633f36de","tid":122303,"uid":21936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啫係咁你個fd去做警察 就即係變左黑警？<br />\n<br />\n理性少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 段友誼咁撚兒戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係連登到討論差人無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 只有一堆盲反"},{"pid":"3f3e2186bfa4835567e11f37c27304a1056966a6","tid":122303,"uid":545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:16:40.000Z","msg":"又唔係當差一定差既<br />\n有個fd因為讀唔成書先去當差，hea吓hea吓就30，40k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b14405be419acec766be09475bd658d492dcd5","tid":122303,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"有個中學同學去左當差 早排死左老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096550c5ad0c44a92287c6e2cf73fcf58f5e6a82","tid":122303,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個中學同學去左當差 早排死左老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\"